68-on-emotions-and-education.title: 68 - On Emotions and Education
68-on-emotions-and-education.description: Reflects on my view on understanding of personality and the capability and motivation to teach/ mentor, with Inside Out 2 and the Korosensei series.

69-personifying-ai.title: 69 - Personiifying AI
69-personifying-ai.description: Summarizes the potential MBTI candidates of AI, using frameworks of MBTI and a related OCEAN research. Goes on to discuss my personality match with AI and embracement to further enhance my edges down the road of being a quant.

70-goodbye-sun.title: 70 - Goodbye Sun
70-goodbye-sun.description: Discusses my Instagram ban in July, and my way forward realizing that social media brings me a degenerating value, and decorrelating is necessary.

71-fermi-estimation.title: 71 - Fermi Estimation
71-fermi-estimation.description: Discusses the background, solving strategies of Fermi Estimations as a modelling device of quantities of life. It goes on to discuss estimation at a greater scope.

72-dice-reroll.title: 72 - Dice Reroll
72-dice-reroll.description: Using dice reroll examples in quant interviews to illustrate optimal choices under dynamic programming, and the destabilizing power of rerolling at a larger scale as a zero-sum game.

73-regularization.title: 73 - Regularization
73-regularization.description: First provides an overview of regularization, then apply the concept of L_p norms to discuss individual preferences, socializing norms, and societal differences.
